org.enterprisedomain.classmaker

Interface Project

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.jobs.ISchedulingRule, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Contribution
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContributionImpl, ProjectImpl

    public interface Project
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.jobs.ISchedulingRule
    A representation of the model object ' Project'. Default project class.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Project Name
    • Children
    • Dirty
    • Workspace
    • Need Completion Notification
    • Completion Notification Adapter
    See Also:
    ClassMakerPackage.getProject()
